      <a name="what"></a> 
      <h5>What is The Daily Grower?</h5>
      <p>
        The <i>The Daily Grower</i> is the home of the best news, articles, vlogs, and recipes for homesteaders, small farmers, and growers of all kinds.
        We curate content from around all the corners of the Internet in one place every day so you don't need have to waste your time clicking and
        scrolling.
      </p>
      <p>
        Best of all, <i>The Daily Grower</i> is <b>crowdsourced</b>. That means that anyone, including YOU, can <a href="{{ internal_pages.contribute }}">contribute</a> to this site and help all
        of us grow. We decided to call it the daily grower to focus on homesteaders and farmers who are growing animals, plants and food, but also everyone who
        is looking to improve anything from health to finances, skillset to mindset. Our goal is for you to grow just a little bit better each day.
      </p>
      <p>
        We also roll the stories featured on the web into a newsletter delivered directly to your inbox for those of you who prefer email.
        It free and easy to join, just visit our <a href="{{ internal_pages.subscribe }}">subscription</a> page and leave your email address. We're having fun
        with it and for our special subscribers, you'll get to see the day's new stories first!
      </p>
    </div>
