      <a name="what"></a>
      <h5>Why The Daily Grower?</h5>
      <p>
      Content curation sites exist in the politics and finances arenas, but not really for homesteaders and small family farms. There is also a TON of
      content out there for those interested in growing their skills. So much that it is easy to get overwhelmed. <i>The Daily Grower</i> is here to
      help you sift through all of that and get the best value for your time scouring the Internet for the best.
      </p>
    </div>
