      <h5>Who is Behind The Daily Grower?</h5>
      <p>
        <i>The Daily Grower</i> was originally contrived by Randy Kleinman, a husband, dad, software engineer, tinkerer, web developer, and regenerative
        farmer. Randy's tends to be a lifelong learner, and loves to research. More of a Jack of All Trades kind of guy, but sometimes lacking a little
        confidence. Encouraged by his friends Justin Rhodes and Aaron Burquest, Randy decided to create <i>The Daily Grower</i> after seeing a need for
        curated content in the homesteading and small farmer space.
